                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Sinmolds are aware that they're in a vulnerable state as formless \"newborn fiends\" and are desperate to become stronger before they become prey to more powerful demons. Whenever the sinmold is in a combat encounter and ends its turn without dealing damage to another creature, the sinmold takes @Damage[3d6[mental]] damage and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>"
                },
