                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[fortitude|dc:32]</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Damage[2d8[poison]] damage (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Damage[3d8[poison]] damage and can hear the thoughts of root rotters within 30 feet as an imprecise sense (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> as stage 2, but @Damage[4d8[poison]] damage and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> as stage 3, and arise as a root rotter upon death (1 round)</p>"
